%h3 Review SSH Keys

%table
  %tr
    %th Name
    %th Belongs To
    %th Controls

  - @ssh_keys.each do |key|
    %tr
      %td= key.name
      %td= key.user ? key.user.email : 'None'
      %td
        = link_to 'Delete', ssh_key_path(key), :method => :delete, :confirm => 'Are you sure you want to remove this SSH key?'
